net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.builder.components

Class WidgetHandlerImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.builder.components.WidgetHandlerImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WidgetHandler

    public class WidgetHandlerImpl
extends Object
implements WidgetHandler
    A simple dummy implementation of the WidgetHandler interface. This class is used by ComponentManagerImpl for the implementation of the getWidgetHandlerFor() method. Most of the methods here simply operate on internal flags and do not have any further effects. The class can be used for testing operations on widgets.
    Version:
    $Id: WidgetHandlerImpl.java 205 2012-01-29 18:29:57Z oheger $
    Author:
    Oliver Heger
